01:23:25,701 --> 01:23:27,233
WHAT? PARIS?

1679
01:23:27,303 --> 01:23:31,705
YES, PARIS.     
                FOR HER.

1680
01:23:31,774 --> 01:23:33,907
YOU SPEAK LIKE THIS             
OF TUCCIO?

1681
01:23:33,975 --> 01:23:36,360
WHAT IS THE LOVE OF SOMEONE 
    LIKE TUCCIO WORTH?

1682
01:23:36,429 --> 01:23:37,844
YOU CLAIM TO BE                 
HIS FRIEND?

1683
01:23:37,913 --> 01:23:40,180
YOU FORGET, DARLING,    
        I'M YOUR FRIEND, TOO.

1684
01:23:40,248 --> 01:23:42,081
